---
// This component outlines the company's process. It is purely presentational.
---
<section id="process" class="py-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="content-plate">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center section-header-glow">Our Streamlined IT Process</h2>
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4 mb-16 text-center">
            We provide clarity and results through a proven, four-step process designed for maximum efficiency and minimal disruption to your business.
        </p>
        <div class="relative">
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-0.5 border-t-2 border-dashed border-[var(--lightest-navy)] -translate-y-1/2"></div>
            <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="tech-card z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-[var(--navy)] text-[var(--cyan)] text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-[var(--cyan)]">1</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl text-center">Discovery</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-center">We start by understanding your business, goals, and existing infrastructure to identify pain points and opportunities.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="tech-card z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-[var(--navy)] text-[var(--cyan)] text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-[var(--cyan)]">2</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl text-center">Strategy</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-center">We design a custom, scalable IT roadmap that aligns with your budget and sets your business up for future growth.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="tech-card z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-[var(--navy)] text-[var(--cyan)] text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-[var(--cyan)]">3</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl text-center">Implementation</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-center">Our expert technicians seamlessly migrate your systems, install new hardware, and deploy solutions with minimal downtime.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="tech-card z-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-[var(--navy)] text-[var(--cyan)] text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4 border-2 border-[var(--cyan)]">4</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl text-center">Support</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-center">We provide ongoing monitoring, maintenance, and help desk support to keep your systems secure and optimized.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>